Title: DevWorldRed Kill Withered at Farm
Description: Travel to DevWorld Farm and eliminate some Withered.
ObjectiveProposalResponse: Greetings, fresh meat. Why don't you go to DevWorld Farm and take out some Withered. If you come back in one piece, your status might be upgraded from fresh meat to rare meat.
InProgressResponse: DevWorld Farm is a dangerous place, I understand if fresh meat like you can't handle it
DestinationCompletionAvailableResponse: Ah yes, you have returned... in one piece, no less... I hearby bestow upon you the title of "rare meat". Congratulations. Now go talk to the artificer to rise one more rank on the meat scale.

Title: DevWorldRed Get Loot at Farm
Description: Search DevWorld Farm and bring back anything you find.
ObjectiveProposalResponse: Greetings, rare meat. You are probably tired of being called that, so I will help you if you help me. I might be able to elevate your status to medium-well meat if you score me some loot from DevWorld Farm.
InProgressResponse: I'm losing patience, and you don't want me to lose my patience. Hurry up and get me that loot.
DestinationCompletionAvailableResponse: Ah I see you have arrived with my loot. I hereby bestow upon you the title of "medium-well meat". You ain't to bad, kid.

Title: Shivering Timbers
Description: Put a stop to the salvage operations at Scavenger's Shore and Bleachwood Coast, and report back to Headman Onizuka in the Reekwater Settlement.
ObjectiveProposalResponse: That's when I hid, but they started getting salvage for those banners from all the wrecks on the shoreline.\n\nIf you really want to gum up her plan, you should strike those salvage operations. Don't come back here, though.
InProgressResponse: I think I'll be staying here. Like I said, it's safer.\n\nI mean you got salt, but if I was a betting woman -  and I am - I'd bet on the Siren Queen. No offense!
DestinationCompletionAvailableResponse: At long last, you return! I was beginning to think you might've joined the Siren Queen's crew!\n\nNow you have seen it with your own eyes, haven't you? She's as much a threat as this Corruption, I tell you.
